A simple ember.js app using grunt for the client side build step


To run the ember.js web app

    npm install
    export PATH="./node_modules/.bin:$PATH"
    grunt
    ./bin/server

    visit http://localhost:3000 to see the running app


To run the javascript tests

    npm install
    export PATH="./node_modules/.bin:$PATH"
    grunt test


Known issues: tests will not work with RC6 just yet

https://github.com/emberjs/ember.js/pull/3026
